data.description: Fully remodeled! Home is surrounded by mature trees and bushes that provides privacy. Features included updated kitchen with quartz countertops, large island, upgraded cabinetry and high end appliances. LVP flooring, neutral paint colors, and updated bathrooms! Primary bedroom includes private ensuite bath with walk in shower and 2 closets. Fully fenced backyard with awning. RV parking on the side. Deep 2 car garage.
